'''[[shooting]] [[star]]'''
# A streak of light in the night sky, caused by a [[meteor]] burning up as it enters the [[Earth]]’s [[atmosphere]].
# The ''[[Dodecatheon]]'' [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]]s.<!--the whole genus or should this be more like "a/any member of..."?-->

